{"tid":1181471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡總理: 阻止中國發展並非明智之舉","createTime":"2019-06-01T15:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T03:49:41.000Z","uid":134071,"like":23,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ca720e91532a97a380233c26dab28e9a249d6b78","tid":1181471,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"有線新聞 i-Cable News<br />\n已讚好的專頁 &middot; 11 小時 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n【李顯龍談及中美關係】 【各國須接受中國繼續壯大】【李顯龍談及中美關係】<br />\n【各國須接受中國繼續壯大】<br />\n<br />\n新加坡總理李顯龍在亞洲安全會議表示，各國必須接受中國繼續壯大的事實，阻止中國發展並非明智之舉。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍指中國在開發本土的高端科技等方面，擁有合法的權益和期望，各國必須在貿易、知識產權、網絡安全及社交媒體等方面，制定新的國際規則，讓中國擁有話語權，如果中美關係持續惡化，對雙方都是嚴重錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/vb.186040714921338/2109565022674804/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2Fvb.186040714921338%2F2109565022674804%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=f299dffc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/vb.186040714921338/2109565022674804/?type=2&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"06329da21b99977743f4a449f61e10b3fee48e9f","tid":1181471,"uid":38904,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"因為支那冇錢大家都冇油水奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533e31652f3b248ba66e53c4c79ef58ad22147f4","tid":1181471,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":25,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"新加坡同大馬都選擇親中<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞: 力挺華為, 美國應對中國讓步<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1178102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1178102/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a3a541fd4c5520c389bd3d0e7d0b757458bb3078","tid":1181471,"uid":173002,"like":65,"dislike":9,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"533e31652